OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,FStable staff have been given enhanced
OL,7,Fracehorse welfare training in an
OL,8,Fattempt to protect the animals during
OL,9,Fthis year's Grand National Festival.
OL,11,FRun by Equi-Ed, an equine therapy
OL,12,Ftraining centre and funded by the
OL,13,FJockey Club, the sessions are part of
OL,14,Fa nationwide scheme to improve
OL,15,Fhandler's physiological understanding
OL,16,Fof the animals and prevent injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,FTraining includes stride length
OL,7,Fanalysis, physical examinations and
OL,8,Fskeletal instruction to equip the
OL,9,Fstaff with specialist knowledge to
OL,10,Fmonitor their horses' physical
OL,11,Fcondition and wellbeing.
OL,13,FStable staff told ITV Granada Reports,
OL,14,Fthe training helped them become more
OL,15,Fobservant of potential issues.
OL,17,F"I've actually really enjoyed it, I
OL,18,Fthought it was really interesting,"
OL,19,FAntonia Heraghty, a Work Rider said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,F"It's just being more aware of things
OL,7,Fbecause you don't want it to get to
OL,8,Fthe point where maybe they're having
OL,9,Fto have time off for it.
OL,11,F"Maybe the saddles not fit quite
OL,12,Fright, but they've been riding in it
OL,13,Ffor a few days now, and now they're
OL,14,Freally sore."
OL,16,FYard Person Craig Simeon added: "I've
OL,17,Fworked in racing for a few years and
OL,18,Fsome things you don't actually know so
OL,19,Fit's good to actually know everyday is
OL,20,Fa learning day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,F"They're such special animals. They're
OL,7,Fso smart a bit like your friends in a
OL,8,Fway. I'll do anything for them."
OL,10,FTherese Murphy, founder of Equi-id, is
OL,11,Fpart of the team giving hands on
OL,12,Ftraining to staff, she said its more
OL,13,Fimportant than ever.
OL,15,F"All eyes are on racing and we all
OL,16,Fneed to do better," Therese Murphy,
OL,17,Ffounder of Equi-id said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,F"To improve welfare we have to focus
OL,7,Fon the people that are with these
OL,8,Fhorses every day and we have to make
OL,9,Fchanges from the ground up.
OL,11,F"If we can make a small change to
OL,12,Fprevent one of these horses being
OL,13,Finjured, that's a win for us."
OL,15,FThe welfare of racehorses at events
OL,16,Flike the Grand National has long been
OL,17,Fa concern among animal rights groups,
OL,18,Fwith many saying the best way to
OL,19,Fprotect them is to ban jump racing
OL,20,Faltogether.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,F'Lawyers for Animal's' campaign lead,
OL,7,FDene Stansall said, "Last year 192
OL,8,Fhorses died on British race courses,
OL,9,Fsomebody has to be held accountable.
OL,11,F"The best way to look after horses, is
OL,12,Fto remove the British Horse Racing
OL,13,FAuthority from their remit of horse
OL,14,Fregulating."
OL,16,FThey are calling for a change in the
OL,17,Flaw so that along with individuals,
OL,18,Forganisations can be held accountable
OL,19,Funder the Animal Welfare Act.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,FHowever The British Horseracing
OL,7,FAuthority argue that the rules of
OL,8,Fracing mean they are held to an even
OL,9,Fhigher standard when it comes to the
OL,10,Fcare for horses.
OL,12,FThe festival suffered the first death
OL,13,Fof the races on 10 April, after Gold
OL,14,FDancer died just moments after winning
OL,15,Fits race in what owners called a
OL,16,F"hollow victory".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
