OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,FThe Willie Mullins-trained seven-year-
OL,7,Fold suffered a fatal injury during the
OL,8,FWilliam Hill Mildmay Novices' Chase at
OL,9,FAintree after landing badly jumping
OL,10,Fthe second fence from home.
OL,12,FHe stayed on his feet and kept going
OL,13,Fto win by four and three-quarter
OL,14,Flengths, but on pulling up it was soon
OL,15,Fclear the winner - who was 100-30
OL,16,Fjoint-favourite - had suffered a
OL,17,Fserious injury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,FThe on-course veterinary team were
OL,7,Fquick to come to his aid, but the
OL,8,Fhorse, who was wearing the colours of
OL,9,FGigginstown House Stud, could not be
OL,10,Fsaved.
OL,12,FThe death means a total of 68 horses
OL,13,Fhave now died at the Aintree Festival
OL,14,Fsince 2000, with figures from Animal
OL,15,FAid showing 17 horses have died after
OL,16,Fracing in the Grand National alone.
OL,18,FWith a global audience of around 600
OL,19,Fmillion, despite the controversy the
OL,20,FGrand National remains one of the most
OL,21,Ficonic horse races in the world.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
