OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776010271
OL,3,CStable staff given horse welfare
OL,4,Ctraining ahead of Grand National
OL,6,FHeld annually at Aintree, The Grand
OL,7,FNational first took place in 1839 and
OL,8,Fhas become one of the most high
OL,9,Fprofile races in the world.
OL,11,FAccording to the The University Campus
OL,12,Fof Football Business, between #250
OL,13,Fmillion and #350 million is wagered on
OL,14,Fthe race each year, with two thirds of
OL,15,Fthose who watched it, placing a bet in
OL,16,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
